Imaxima
*******

Imaxima is a package for displaying the output from the computer
algebra system Maxima as images typeset by TeX.

This manual documents imaxima version 5.38.1. You can download the
latest version of imaxima from
`http://members3.jcom.home.ne.jp/imaxima/'.

Since version 1.0b, imaxima and imath supports inline graph.

Send suggestions and bug reports to Yasuaki Honda <imaxima@mac.com>.

